query:
SELECT 
  address,
  COUNT(*) as count,
  GROUP_CONCAT(id ORDER BY id) as ids,
  GROUP_CONCAT(leadId ORDER BY leadId) as leadIds
FROM properties
WHERE address IS NOT NULL AND address != ''
GROUP BY address
HAVING count > 1
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 20;
